'''-{zh-hans:卡倫·安妮·布拉德利; zh-hk:龐碧琳;}-'''（{{lang-en|Karen Anne Bradley}}<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=59418 |date=13 May 2010 |startpage=8745}}</ref>；{{bd|1970年|3月12日||catIdx=B}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/41311.stm |title=Karen Bradley MP |publisher=BBC |work=BBC Democracy Live |date= |accessdate=25 July 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305021906/http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/41311.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>）
，是[[保守黨_(英國)|英國保守黨]]的黨員，自[[2010年英國大選|2010年英國大選]]當選[[斯塔福德郡穆爾蘭茲_(英國國會選區)|斯塔福德郡穆爾蘭茲選區]]的[[英國下議院|下議院]][[國會議員|議員]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.staffsmoorlands.gov.uk/downloads/Declaration_RESULT_Parl_2010.doc |title=Staffordshire Moorlands District Council election results |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2011-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613203317/http://www.staffsmoorlands.gov.uk/downloads/Declaration_RESULT_Parl_2010.doc |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/news/Elections-2010-Karen-Bradley-takes-Staffordshire-Moorlands-6-700-majority/article-2128276-detail/article.html Elections 2010: Karen Bradley takes Staffordshire Moorlands with 6,700 majority] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/news/Elections-2010-Karen-Bradley-takes-Staffordshire-Moorlands-6-700-majority/article-2128276-detail/article.html |date=20100510015021 }} on ThisIsStaffordshire.co.uk</ref>。2012年9月，她被任命為政府黨鞭辦公室助理[[黨鞭|政府黨鞭]]<ref>[http://www.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/content/list-government-departments-and-ministers "List of Government departments and ministers"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/content/list-government-departments-and-ministers |date=20130117055936 }}, Cabinet Office, 6 September 2012</ref>；到2013年晉升成為政府黨鞭（助理財政大臣；{{lang|en|Junior Lord of the Treasury}}）<ref name=gov-uk>{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/people/karen-bradley |title=Karen Bradley MP |website=GOV.UK |accessdate=13 September 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906101735/https://www.gov.uk/government/people/karen-bradley |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年7月，新任首相[[文翠珊|文翠珊]]任命龐碧琳為[[數碼、文化、傳媒及體育大臣|文化傳媒及體育大臣]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-07-14/karen-bradley-is-new-culture-secretary-as-john-whittingdale-is-sacked |title=Karen Bradley is new culture secretary as John Whittingdale is sacked |access-date=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519090148/https://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-07-14/karen-bradley-is-new-culture-secretary-as-john-whittingdale-is-sacked/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

